                                                     Sachin, Yuvraj advice for colts
                  Sachin                     
	Senior-most pro Sachin Tendulkar and ODI vice-captain Yuvraj Singh, a member of the 1999-00 U-19 World Cup-winning squad, wished Virat Kohli and his boys all the very best for Sundays final against Pakistan/South Africa. They spoke after Friday evenings nets at the SCG.         
	The following are excerpts:         
	SACHIN: Our juniors should enjoy the final, enjoy the moment... Our good wishes are with them. The hope is that theyll return home with the World Cup.         
	YUVRAJ: Its such an important tournament for the emerging players... Im delighted that were in yet another final and Im looking forward to one more World Cup coming our way.                 OUR SPECIAL CORRESPONDENT IN SYDNEY                                                                                                                   
